    "causal_summary": "Phase 13 of the 026 graph-and-context-optimization wrapper. The 010-graph-impact and 011-cocoindex-daemon and 012-causal-graph wrappers added the underlying systems (causal trust display, daemon resilience, channel routing); this phase exposes them as doctor commands so users can rebuild + maintain them via the standard `/doctor:*` surface. Closes the gap left by v3.4.1.0 which shipped the doctor pattern for `code-graph`, `skill-advisor`, `skill-budget`, `mcp_install`, and `mcp_debug` but not the four other databases.",
